Game.Controller

Class MapEditorController

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game.Controller.MapEditorController

  • public class MapEditorController
extends java.lang.Object
    The controller for the Map Editor view. It handles the data flown inside the map editor view. The controller can manage the new map and load the existing map.
    Version:
    1.2.0
    Author:
    ndkcha
